Building Bitcashcoins

See doc/readme-qt.md for instructions on building Bitcashcoins-Qt,
the intended-for-end-users, nice-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Bitcashcoins.

See doc/build-*.md for instructions on building bitcashcoinsd,
the intended-for-services, no-graphical-interface, reference
implementation of Bitcashcoins.